  "description": "<p>Climbing tomorrow, hiking next weekend, dream backpacking trip in a few months... playing outdoors can get complicated. Simplify things a bit with these versatile soft shell pants. Tough, lightweight and beautifully constructed, the Gamma pants have you covered for a wide range of activities. They're cut to accommodate dynamic movements, with articulated tailoring and plenty of stretch. The fit is close to the body with a straight leg, with a low profile brushed-back waistband that lies comfortably under a pack. Drawstring adjustable cuffs can be tightened to keep out bugs and trail debris, or hiked up out of the way for climbing.</p><ul><li>Fortius\u2122 DW 2.0 fabric is lightweight, durable and DWR-treated for water resistance</li><li>Soft, brushed polyester-lined waist has a snap closure and integrated adjustable webbing belt</li><li>Low-profile waistbelt rides comfortably under a harness or pack</li><li>Two zippered hand pockets and thigh pocket keeps essentials on hand</li><li>Gusseted crotch, articulated knee and stretch for freedom of movement</li><li>Adjustable drawcord pant cuffs</li></ul>",
